  code: 2A
  story: "Cinder allowed the slipper to be tried, and it fit perfectly. His hidden
    identity was revealed before his stepfamily could interfere. When Elara arrived,
    recognition came not from appearance alone, but from the quiet presence remembered
    from the ball. \n\nCinder\u2019s honesty and humility outweighed his lack of
    status. Taken to the palace, he was no longer defined by hardship but by character.
    His past remained part of him, but it no longer controlled his future. In choosing
    to be seen, he gained both freedom and belonging in a world that finally acknowledged
    his worth."
